meanings.meaning: live, etc. to tell the tale

vlive.korean: 그렇습니다. - 물론 전 살아남지 않았지만 여러분은 살아남았죠? That's right! - Of course, I didn't survive, but all of you did, right? 듣기 View video PENTAGON : [펜타곤 교과서 시즌5] EP. 1 - 발표 시간
vlive.english: That's right! - Of course, I didn't survive, but all of you did, right?

vlive.korean: "잘해야 살아남지"로 바꿔! "Only better one lives to tell the tale"! 듣기 View video KNK : 지금 크나큰(KNK)은?
vlive.english: "Only better one lives to tell the tale"!

vlive.korean: 그래서 어느 한 캐릭터도 살아남지 못한 거죠. That's why nobody can survive. 듣기 View video 10PM : 김태훈, 정시우의 무비톡톡! Movie talk!talk!
우와. 잘해야만 살아남지. - 수능 지나고 아닐 수도 있어요. Wow. Only better one lives to tell the tale. - I don't know when we'll be back clearly. 듣기 View video KNK : 지금 크나큰(KNK)은?
vlive.english: Wow. Only better one lives to tell the tale. - I don't know when we'll be back clearly.

vlive.korean: 약하면 살아남지 못해. "It preys on the weak". 듣기 View video 10PM : 목요일 김태훈, 정시우의 무비톡톡! Movie talk!talk!

examples.korean: Nobody survived the massacre. 발음듣기 아무도 그 대학살에서 살아남지 못했다. Oxford Advanced Learner's English-Korean Dictionary
Many women also do not survive complications affected by pregnancy and childbirth. 발음듣기 많은 여성들 역시 임신과 출산으로 인한 합병증으로 살아남지 못하고 있습니다. YBM All in All English-Korean Dictionary
examples.english: Many women also do not survive complications affected by pregnancy and childbirth. 발음

examples.korean: A lazy bum cannot survive even in the marketplace. 발음듣기 게으른 건달은 장터에서조차 살아 남지 못한다. YBM All in All English-Korean Dictionary
examples.english: A lazy bum cannot survive even in the marketplace. 발음

examples.korean: Many worried fans think that this is a hint that Harry Potter won't survive the final book. 발음듣기 우려하는 많은 팬들은 이것이 해리포터가 마지막 책에서 살아남지 못한다는 암시라고 생각한다. Neungyule
examples.english: Many worried fans think that this is a hint that Harry Potter won't survive the final book. 발음

examples.korean: The earth is approaching another iceage and his species will not survive. 발음듣기 지구에는 다시 빙하기가 오고 있는데 이 종족은 살아남지 못할꺼야. Neungyule
examples.english: The earth is approaching another iceage and his species will not survive. 발음
